# Optional: provide a Claude API key so the app can call the real model on startup.
# You can also paste a key at runtime via the in-app Settings dialog (stored in
# your browser's localStorage only — never sent anywhere except Anthropic's API).
#
# Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com/
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in your key:
VITE_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
